headline: 3 Consumer Stocks in Hot Water
summary: The performance of consumer discretionary businesses is closely linked to economic cycles. Thankfully for the industry, demand trends seem to be healthy as discretionary stocks have gained 6.1% over the past six months. This performance has nearly mirrored the S&P 500.
